Honey STOP the CAR!! Come Say Yes to this  MOVE IN READY Address!! 
Enjoy this Newly Renovated Modern Dream Home located in the heart of Garland with everything you need to keep life simple close by.
Go for a walk at the nearby parks, enjoy shopping, dining, entertainment, easy access to Hwys. Great neighborhood with mature shade trees and great schools nearby. Impress family& friends by hosting celebrations & events in the 2 large living areas, 2nd area opens to the newly renovated kitchen with a gourmet island, new staineless steel appliances,walk in pantry for storing all the goodies and extras, private laundry space to keep things tidy, built in wine center for Wine Down time, a private coverd patio and nice sized back yard for the kiddos and fur friends to run and play. This home has it ALL! 
Seller is Motivated and ready to consider the right offer! $2500 Grant Eligible for Closing Cost!
